result.name: BURGER KITCHEN

reviews.text: lunch 幾低食，60唔洗但食到好juicy 既漢堡
The burgers are considered tasty and have varieties of choices to your liking. The prices are acceptably fair. The burgers are so made with a touch of European style ! These are my cup of tea !
Latte咖啡夠滑， 春卷，雞翼都唔錯， 晏晝跟餐沙律夠多菜同埋湯好足磨菇料。藍莓奶昔有d似藥水味，包有點干，如果人多果時，走廊有點逼，打卡影相放fb, ig優惠95折唔太顯眼
大埔少數的Burger店。有Lunch Set，可選餐湯或沙律。蜆肉忌廉湯不錯！漢堡包跟熱辣辣薯條，加埋凍飲都比外國吃便宜。而且Beef w/ Spam Burger午餐肉用上外國品牌SPAM，抵食，有質素！卡邦尼意粉啲汁好入味，意粉選用幼細既麵條好好咬。另點一杯凍Matcha Latte要加15蚊。抹茶粉很多，所以味道有點苦澀。唯一係間餐廳細左少少，否則係聚腳吹水好地方。
They serve the best burgers in a fairly cheap price at Sai Kung

result.name: Eightland Gardens

reviews.text: One of the oldest residential site right at the centre of Tai Po. You can have free shuttle buses to the Tai Po Train station. It is also a 5 mins walk to the Tai Po terminus where you can find buses to other urban areas in Hong Kong Island and Kowloon. There are also many good restaurants nearby.
very nice place  👍
Have free shuttle bus to theTai Po Railway station.
Nice place with good restaurant

reviews.text: 路边花草幾靚。超市、藥房、及幾間食店都有捧場者。
交通方便，樓下就大把食店同車站，而且有通消小巴出深水埗同旺角。😎
這個私人屋琬，唔錯，有小舊，交通方便，住得過。
